    "TAM has been studied in a variety of situations and contexts, including in university education, online learning and secondary education (Wojciechowski & Cellary, 2013).",
    "Perceived usefulness (PU), perceived ease-of-use (PEOU), attitude toward usage (ATT), and behavioral intention to use (BI) are the four dimensions that TAM suggests.",
    "Additionally, \"trust\" has been included as a new variable to the model.",
    "To ascertain the needs and directions for future study, it is therefore imperative to discuss the problems and difficulties related to TAM.",
    "Consequently, several researchers have proposed adding other factors to TAM."
